high_descs: Move to the sink.
Open up the right drawer and pick up the soap in the drawer.
Bring the soap over to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank lid.
Move over to the sink.
Pick up the soap next to the sink.
Bring the soap over to the toilet.
Put the soap on the toilet tank lid next to the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: walk to the bathroom sink in front of you
open the cabinet on the right side below and pick up the soap dispenser
walk over to face the toilet
place the soap dispenser on top of the toilet
walk back over to the bathroom sink
pick up the soap dispenser off of the bathroom counter
walk over to the the toilet again
put the soap dispenser on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: put both of the soap dispensers on top of the toilet

high_descs: Turn right, move to the right hand sink.
Open the cabinet below the sink, pick up the liquid soap container.
Turn left, move to the toilet.
Place the liquid soap container on top of the toilet tank.
Turn right, move to the right hand sink.
Pick up the liquid soap container from the counter.
Turn left, move to the toilet.
Place the liquid soap container on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place liquid soap containers onto the top of the toilet.

high_descs: Approach the sink in front of you.
Remove the soap from the rightmost cabinet under the sink.
Turn around, then turn right, then go right again to face the space between the sink and the toilet.
Place the soap on the back of the toilet, in front of the bar soap.
Turn right, go straight, then turn left at the sink on the right.
Pick up the soap from the right of the sink.
Turn around, then turn right, then go right again to face the space between the sink and the toilet.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet, to the left of the bar soap.
anns.task_desc: Put two soaps on the back of the toilet.
